data.description: Embrace the comfort of modern living in this updated three-family home, each unit featuring one bedroom, central air, and forced hot air heating for year-round comfort. With updated electricals and tankless Rheem water heaters, enjoy the efficiency and convenience of contemporary amenities. Situated in the sought-after Forest Hills neighborhood, this property is ideal for investors or those seeking a multi-unit home in a tranquil, yet connected area. Experience the blend of peaceful living with the vibrancy of Newark's community
